"type":"subtitle_en"},{"data":{"duration":2.952,"path":"https://lf26-appstore-sign.oceancloudapi.com/ocean-cloud-tos/VolcanoUserVoice/speech_7426720361732980745_0933e134-ca74-4d3f-838f-285f8de779c4.mp3?lk3s=da27ec82&x-expires=1762178060&x-signature=5OF8PNTkvUQoXrE8bvQTCmWD5R0%3D","start":14.668},"type":"voice"},{"data":{"duration":2.952,"start":14.668,"text":"明明没做错事却总觉得自己搞砸了"},"type":"subtitle"},{"data":{"duration":2.952,"start":14.668},"type":"subtitle_en"},{"data":{"duration":2.448,"path":"https://lf6-appstore-sign.oceancloudapi.com/ocean-cloud-tos/VolcanoUserVoice/speech_7426720361732980745_b8bdf150-0581-4674-bb51-bf50a69cf557.mp3?lk3s=da27ec82&x-expires=1762178060&x-signature=X76aZpzbuEuGcATOfgJhxbV29ws%3D","start":17.62},"type":"voice"},{"data":{"duration":2.448,"start":17.62,"text":"甚至会因为别人一个眼神"},"type":"subtitle"},{"data":{"duration":2.448,"start":17.62},"type":"subtitle_en"},{"data":{"duration":2.664,"path":"https://lf9-appstore-sign.oceancloudapi.com/ocean-cloud-tos/VolcanoUserVoice/speech_7426720361732980745_d9faf3fb-52cc-4158-b76e-4066af70bae9.mp3?lk3s=da27ec82&x-expires=1762178060&x-signature=iRn8RA39NK%2FamDRkQhna9FZX3so%3D","start":20.068},"type":"voice"},{"data":{"duration":2.664,"start":20.068,"text":"在心里演完一整部情感大戏"},"type":"subtitle"},{"data":{"duration":2.664,"start":20.068},"type":"subtitle_en"},{"data":{"duration":2.808,"path":"https://lf9-appstore-sign.oceancloudapi.com/ocean-cloud-tos/VolcanoUserVoice/speech_7426720361732980745_7ef6894f-70ce-4b2d-b957-11d419f716c7.mp3?lk3s=da27ec82&x-expires=1762178061&x-signature=21drE0vUZE3O7SiSJqU%2Brot3LDg%3D","start":22.732000000000003},"type":"voice"},{"data":{"duration":2.808,"start":22.732000000000003,"text":"你不是想太多，也不是太敏感"},"type":"subtitle"},{"data":{"duration":2.808,"start":22.732000000000003},"type":"subtitle_en"},{"data":{"duration":3.744,"path":"https://lf6-appstore-sign.oceancloudapi.com/ocean-cloud-tos/VolcanoUserVoice/speech_7426720361732980745_bf662cff-1d22-4e76-8cbd-dbe8eb259094.mp3?lk3s=da27ec82&x-expires=1762178062&x-signature=0sOfL7Dy%2F7K3b3wfylPr8u513yE%3D","start":25.540000000000003},"type":"voice"},{"data":{"duration":3.744,"start":25.540000000000003,"text":"你只是比别人更在意感受，更习惯向内思考"},"type":"subtitle"},{"data":{"duration":3.744,"start":25.540000000000003},"type":"subtitle_en"},{"data":{"duration":4.008,"path":"https://lf6-appstore-sign.oceancloudapi.com/ocean-cloud-tos/VolcanoUserVoice/speech_7426720361732980745_5c63994c-5ebf-45f2-9848-e6a1df005b47.mp3?lk3s=da27ec82&x-expires=1762178062&x-signature=YQSMK6nIrV1OKU5BEzy2sGE6VH4%3D","start":29.284},"type":"voice"},{"data":{"duration":4.008,"start":29.284,"text":"在心理学上，这可能被称为“认知反刍”"},"type":"subtitle"},{"data":{"duration":4.008,"start":29.284},"type":"subtitle_en"},{"data":{"duration":4.872,"path":"https://lf3-appstore-sign.oceancloudapi.com/ocean-cloud-tos/VolcanoUserVoice/speech_7426720361732980745_3a51f100-03aa-47ca-b034-d8c6931083a1.mp3?lk3s=da27ec82&x-expires=1762178064&x-signature=ZR5v5JVXWmzKFPA6HMOZY2Ywxvw%3D","start":33.292},"type":"voice"},{"data":{"duration":4.872,"start":33.292,"text":"简单说就是反复咀嚼负面情绪，在脑海里循环回放"},"type":"subtitle"},{"data":{"duration":4.872,"start":33.292},"type":"subtitle_en"},{"data":{"duration":3.36,"path":"https://lf9-appstore-sign.oceancloudapi.com/ocean-cloud-tos/VolcanoUserVoice/speech_7426720361732980745_e006029f-2c08-46e4-ad2a-0620f7a4ef50.mp3?lk3s=da27ec82&x-expires=1762178065&x-signature=Wft8BlxRAbI0qEHybVlVBreq3Qc%3D","start":38.164},"type":"voice"},{"data":{"duration":3.36,"start":38.164,"text":"这或许源于小时候总被要求“懂事”"},"type":"subtitle"},{"data":{"duration":3.36,"start":38.164},"type":"subtitle_en"},{"data":{"duration":3.456,"path":"https://lf3-appstore-sign.oceancloudapi.com/ocean-cloud-tos/VolcanoUserVoice/speech_7426720361732980745_e77230a7-27fa-49ba-93db-c9ad8fa05215.mp3?lk3s=da27ec82&x-expires=1762178063&x-signature=LH4f4ZB5sQpXzPkVdOxOmVt%2Fsg0%3D","start":41.524},"type":"voice"},{"data":{"duration":3.456,"start":41.524,"text":"习惯了先考虑别人的感受，忽略自己的情绪"},"type":"subtitle"},{"data":{"duration":3.456,"start":41.524},"type":"subtitle_en"},{"data":{"duration":2.856,"path":"https://lf3-appstore-sign.oceancloudapi.com/ocean-cloud-tos/VolcanoUserVoice/speech_7426720361732980745_60f871b2-3573-4831-b1e4-6869a4370e0b.mp3?lk3s=da27ec82&x-expires=1762178066&x-signature=94SsoX58GTbBBmGHbeeEo61oOvo%3D","start":44.98},"type":"voice"},{"data":{"duration":2.856,"start":44.98,"text":"也可能是成长中经历过被否定"},"type":"subtitle"},{"data":{"duration":2.856,"start":44.98},"type":"subtitle_en"},{"data":{"duration":3.696,"path":"https://lf26-appstore-sign.oceancloudapi.com/ocean-cloud-tos/VolcanoUserVoice/speech_7426720361732980745_5b6155e0-5a77-45a8-9779-88334e921245.mp3?lk3s=da27ec82&x-expires=1762178066&x-signature=M5qFOmIzOq5NV%2FiMn%2FU0ZAw%2BO00%3D","start":47.836000000000006},"type":"voice"},{"data":{"duration":3.696,"start":47.836000000000006,"text":"所以总忍不住自我检查，生怕哪里做得不好"},"type":"subtitle"},{"data":{"duration":3.696,"start":47.836000000000006},"type":"subtitle_en"},{"data":{"duration":4.752,"path":"https://lf9-appstore-sign.oceancloudapi.com/ocean-cloud-tos/VolcanoUserVoice/speech_7426720361732980745_a27a7e5a-89d1-4ae1-9552-8ed6177ad4db.mp3?lk3s=da27ec82&x-expires=1762178066&x-signature=urv1Crta9WOCosuD1EgsczJskw0%3D","start":51.532},"type":"voice"},{"data":{"duration":4.752,"start":51.532,"text":"但你的敏感不是缺点，是你能细腻感知他人情绪的天赋"},"type":"subtitle"},{"data":{"duration":4.752,"start":51.532},"type":"subtitle_en"},{"data":{"duration":5.256,"path":"https://lf3-appstore-sign.oceancloudapi.com/ocean-cloud-tos/VolcanoUserVoice/speech_7426720361732980745_ada8002c-e899-46ca-8595-f7e12038e67f.mp3?lk3s=da27ec82&x-expires=1762178068&x-signature=d3ekXiu7UaBHitj6MX%2Fd0tsSLAo%3D","start":56.284000000000006},"type":"voice"},{"data":{"duration":5.256,"start":56.284000000000006,"text":"你的“想太多”，其实是你拥有深度思考和共情能力的表现"},"type":"subtitle"},{"data":{"duration":5.256,"start":56.284000000000006},"type":"subtitle_en"},{"data":{"duration":5.304,"path":"https://lf3-appstore-sign.oceancloudapi.com/ocean-cloud-tos/VolcanoUserVoice/speech_7426720361732980745_d56c2be0-eacd-41c7-85de-932d8af869d5.mp3?lk3s=da27ec82&x-expires=1762178068&x-signature=yF2rlBiwM5SPKUZ9Ql159CGHBrw%3D","start":61.540000000000006},"type":"voice"},{"data":{"duration":5.304,"start":61.540000000000006,"text":"它让你更懂得体谅，也让你更能提前规避人际中的暗礁"},"type":"subtitle"},{"data":{"duration":5.304,"start":61.540000000000006},"type":"subtitle_en"},{"data":{"duration":2.952,"path":"https://lf6-appstore-sign.oceancloudapi.com/ocean-cloud-tos/VolcanoUserVoice/speech_7426720361732980745_f50d78a4-6521-4257-8848-26f5d68e27c8.mp3?lk3s=da27ec82&x-expires=1762178068&x-signature=U68trWlyJcfeFHRBmoah3IBpAx4%3D","start":66.84400000000001},"type":"voice"},{"data":{"duration":2.952,"start":66.84400000000001,"text":"你可以试试每天留5分钟“情绪日记”"},"type":"subtitle"},{"data":{"duration":2.952,"start":66.84400000000001},"type":"subtitle_en"},{"data":{"duration":2.904,"path":"https://lf26-appstore-sign.oceancloudapi.com/ocean-cloud-tos/VolcanoUserVoice/speech_7426720361732980745_acdb9b02-59d9-4a59-ba68-f1ff8a975988.mp3?lk3s=da27ec82&x-expires=1762178069&x-signature=m2N%2Fo7l3W87susbMBXiyBC2QLwQ%3D","start":69.796},"type":"voice"},{"data":{"duration":2.904,"start":69.796,"text":"写下纠结的事和自己的答案"},"type":"subtitle"},{"data":{"duration":2.904,"start":69.796},"type":"subtitle_en"},{"data":{"duration":4.824,"path":"https://lf26-appstore-sign.oceancloudapi.com/ocean-cloud-tos/VolcanoUserVoice/speech_7426720361732980745_782016bd-b2ba-4c90-b98a-ebf4b21a5e1e.mp3?lk3s=da27ec82&x-expires=1762178070&x-signature=GLB7jnjT6gi3GUsyCMD1ZiYnbdE%3D","start":72.7},"type":"voice"},{"data":{"duration":4.824,"start":72.7,"text":"当开始反复想时，问自己“这件事对我3年后重要吗”"},"type":"subtitle"},{"data":{"duration":4.824,"start":72.7},"type":"subtitle_en"},{"data":{"duration":5.232,"path":"https://lf26-appstore-sign.oceancloudapi.com/ocean-cloud-tos/VolcanoUserVoice/speech_7426720361732980745_80fe21e1-d594-40ed-b795-6aaee1e97ff6.mp3?lk3s=da27ec82&x-expires=1762178070&x-signature=cf
